Edit2 : I only play on enquea because of site 7 ^^, i prefer playing shadow between and legolas to cycle in fellow, threats are only support but you re right when you say i have to add more threat tokens, if gala is the ring bearer , i can not play nenya too , can i ?<br />
<br />
Edit3 :Corsairs are ripped off by farabow and archery, more over there is derufin, swarms suffer from archery fire, discard and company of archers, and threat nazgul are not a pb with big glorfi and archery fire :)<br />
<br />
Seriously this deck is really interesting to play and is able to do sthg :)<br />
<br />
The fellow part is classic gondelf with a few adaptations because of reflections : for exple, the ring bearer i chose is galadriel because she can become a support archer or a discard machine by using white arrows. About glorfi i can&#39;t imagine a elf deck without him, he is too strong!!!<br />
<br />
Except those cards, this fellow is able to resist against most of shadows (derufin and shadow between, massiv archery and healing, sam for burden removal,company of archer for condition removal, Faramir for pump minions etc...)<br />
<br />
The shadow is a bit strange for nazzies threat because i don&#39;t use gollum, but what you must understand is that threat tokens are just a backup for a nazgul beatdown blade tip deck, and for those who thought i couldn&#39;t cycle quickly, try to use legolas special ability ^^<br />
<br />
Against gdlf , play too great ; against rohan use black fail; against DH throw away conditions and event and against Ent saved deck just enjoy :) and maybe play sauron mouhahahahah ^^<br />
<br />
Have fun !<br />
